    "description": "<p>Headquartered in Singapore, ICPM is a one-stop AIDC &amp; RFID system integration provider. We provide integrated hardware and software solutions, to empower customer success in integrated supply chain solutions.</p>\n<p>ICPM partners with industry leaders in the AIDC &amp; RFID space to deliver continuing excellence for customers.</p>\n<p>ICPM is the sole channel distributor for Chainway’s retail- and logistics-optimised mobile computing and RFID products, and the authorized distributor for Zebra, GoDex, Scanalogic , Postek , Matica TM, E-com, Novexx, Honeywell, TP Link, Brohter, Seuic, etc.</p>\n<p>As the authorized distributor for our technology partners, ICPM provides competent and timely maintenance services for all products we distribute. Only original parts are used to ensure value and reliable performance.</p>",
